snippet.textDisplay: It's amazing the lengths people will go to defend and justify the actions of a woman who abuses her husband. Mr. Depp has been raked over the coals repeatedly in the public domain based solely upon unsubstantiated accusations. The only reason he's now gaining support is that he kept his recordings and they eventually were leaked to the public. The people who have, in the light of this leak, whom have "switched sides" should really learn a valuable lesson while eating their crow. Due Process matters. Just because the person making the accusation lacks a Y Chromosome does NOT mean they are incapable of lying. Things to consider going forward.
